hr.ques: Tell me about yourself.
What are your strengths and weaknesses?
Why do you want to work at our company?
Where do you see yourself in 5 years?
Why should we hire you?
Can you describe a challenging situation and how you handled it?
What do you know about our company?
What motivates you?
How do you handle stress and pressure?
Do you have any quess for us?
Can you tell me about a time you demonstrated leadership skills?
What is your greatest professional achievement?
How do you prioritize your tasks when working on multiple projects?
Describe a time you failed and how you handled it.
What kind of work environment do you prefer?
How do you handle feedback or criticism?
What are your salary expectations?
Can you explain any gaps in your employment history?
What do you do to maintain work-life balance?
Have you ever had a conflict with a coworker? How did you resolve it?
